at the lying in state ceremony in Caracas’s East Cemetery today.

'We
 will discuss it with her family once the parents have been seen off 
properly,' he said. 'For the moment Maya is staying with some of Monica’s
 cousins in Caracas. The most important thing is that she is safe'.

