'She loved her country too much,' said her brother, Ricardo. 'It was her home.'

Her ex-husband shared her passion for Venezuela and worked as an adventure tour operator.

He moved to the U.S. about 15 years ago after being shot, but returned to Venezuela in 2006, his business partner said.

